World
Traveller
well-being
in the air
Our Well-being in the Air menu offers you a refreshing
dining alternative. As part of the British Airways
Well-being in the Air programme, these dishes are made
from the freshest ingredients. They are designed to be
light and easily digested, and are based on our
new healthy style of inflight dining.
The type of dishes we recommend are
selections from the following:
Salads
Fresh fruit
Poultry and fish based dishes
Pulses, grains, rice and similar accompaniments
Vegetarian options
Wholemeal breads
